From 6eeee2a20ffb2be3456ae8615b227c78e1ca8a20 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Arthur Schiwon <blizzz@arthur-schiwon.de>
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 2025 20:39:05 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] fix: convert implicit null in generated functions

done with:

ack -l '[\( ]{1,1}[a-zA-Z]+ [&]{0,1}\$[a-zA-Z-_]+ = null' generated/ | xargs -n1 sed -i -E 's/([\( ]{1,1})([a-zA-Z]+ [&]{0,1}\$[a-zA-Z\-_]+ = null)/\1?\2/g'

Signed-off-by: Arthur Schiwon <blizzz@arthur-schiwon.de>
